java.lang.Object
org.rdftocsvconverter.RDFtoCSVW.service.RDFtoCSVWService
@Service public class RDFtoCSVWService extends Object
The class methods that handles API to RDFtoCSV library communication and parameter conversion.

    • getCSVString

      public String getCSVString(String url, Map<String,String> config) throws IOException
      This method returns only CSV string, no metadata, and it is not in .zip. This method is only possible with RDF file URL. If multiple files are requested, it will put the CSVs into one string and divide them with visible horizontal delimiter.
      Parameters:
      url - the url
      config - the config
      Returns:
      csv string
      Throws:
      IOException - the io exception

      public Map<String,String> prepareConfigParameter(String table, String conversionMethod, Boolean firstNormalForm)

      table - the table parameter (ONE/MORE)
      conversionMethod - the conversion method parameter (RDF4J/STREAMING/BIGFILESTREAMING)
      firstNormalForm - the first normal form - true if first normal form is to be activated
      Returns:
      the configuration map of parameters for the conversion
